{"tid":972011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鋼筋「肥佬」多　陳帆：或增開鑿位","createTime":"2019-01-07T05:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T06:21:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae53b6894abcd7d301c9bafccedbb92bfad03bf","tid":972011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190107/20585340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F20585340&d=CLvBSNi7HEDZp085ZmrW7smB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=edf492ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F20585340&h=a9685db8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190107/20585340</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月07日 <br />\n<br />\n鋼筋「肥佬」多　陳帆：或增開鑿位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190107/large/19025516.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190107%2Flarge%2F19025516.jpg&h=9ca108d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳帆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【豆腐沙中綫】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵正鑿開紅磡站層板石屎，以超聲波儀器抽驗鋼筋與螺絲帽接駁，多次發現有螺絲帽接駁不達標。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆指，當局早已預期會出現有關狀況，又指若情況不理想，會開鑿更多位置。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指早料有不理想情況<br />\n<br />\n陳帆昨出席活動後指，有關紅磡站的全面評估和調查工作是分階段進行，而過去一段時間開鑿一定數量位置時，發現不同位置有不同情況，是當局早已預期會出現的狀況。他指第二階段工作中會開鑿至少168個位置，表明若情況不理想，會開鑿更多位置。<br />\n<br />\n陳又指當局仍需等待開鑿完成，下階段將進行科學評估和計算工作，再決定是否需要加固月台或其他工作，呼籲外界給予時間。據路政署公佈紅磡站層板石屎檢測結果，截至上周五累積完成39個螺絲帽接駁位置檢測，有12個位置不合格，比率為31%，更發現有完全沒有接駁的鋼筋和絲帽。<br />\n<br />\n沙中綫紅磡站調查委員會上月完成事實證人作供後休庭，周三將在前荃灣裁判法院大樓恢復聆訊，由委員會委聘的專家證人作供。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n村選惡鬥　陳金華再斥兒子打壓<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n郭卓堅去信廉署　促立案查鄭若驊"},{"pid":"87420d6c836171028e91b97c828e0f0b37cf4fe4","tid":972011,"uid":59567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"直接唔計failed咪仲好"},{"pid":"f9feb7702621dfbb2ce31fbfc7d57e1108aba669","tid":972011,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"拆撚咗去啦"},{"pid":"65a17c4ec382e05fbc0f812e7eb1f08641b98c91","tid":972011,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"咁搞法直接搵啲得既仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4053d13bb3615fe5973a61667236aedaddd93f6","tid":972011,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"越搵越多"},{"pid":"ac3f9e04f8babb2d428c0c6169bc8ea66ad7cc77","tid":972011,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"拖時間度故仔降標準"},{"pid":"7d5c7c4010004ea1fe535284867864803d8b5e15","tid":972011,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"想搵d一定無事嘅位黎抽去加大個sample size 同拉低奶野%<br />\n<br />\n但可能會愈搵愈多<br />\n<br />\n不如直接一句 ：「我話ok就ok啦」"},{"pid":"039693f9caed354242240d9ff3bb47915448ff16","tid":972011,"uid":6222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"達哥:依鋪唔計 下次一命爆機"},{"pid":"77e045a8a28dccf738825f6be2a5eb55cac87238","tid":972011,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"情況唔理想就增開鑿位<br />\n想搏開多啲合格率高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加鑿完都唔夠係米再加鑿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話趕著通車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f98d0bd6dee8aa9a62409693e6771455b6af99","tid":972011,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"即係代表佢已經搵到邊幾段係完全冇問題，任人驗？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3b87981d5de90991b8e1531630a66c2b041428","tid":972011,"uid":55614,